queries.sql: SELECT `es3`.`nama_es3`, COUNT(DISTINCT ia.id) as jumlah_item_aktif, COUNT(DISTINCT ii.id) as jumlah_item_inaktif FROM `unit_kerja_es3` as `es3` LEFT JOIN `item_aktif` as `ia` ON `ia`.`id_es3` = `es3`.`id` LEFT JOIN `item_inaktif` as `ii` ON `ii`.`id_es3` = `es3`.`id` WHERE `es3`.`id_es2` = '71' GROUP BY `es3`.`id`, `es3`.`nama_es3` ORDER BY `es3`.`nama_es3` ASC
